    <p>
      <font size="4"><b>Private Peripheral Interrupt (PPI)</b></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;This is a peripheral interrupt that is specific to a single processor.
    </p>
    <p>
